content:
Analyze Your Data

Salesforce Analytics Tools include Reports and Dashboards, Data Cloud Reports and Dashboards, CRM Analytics, Intelligent Analytics Apps, Tableau, Einstein Discovery.

Tableau is a complete analytics platform for harmonizing, managing, and exploring data with interactive visualizations. It can combine and manage data from multiple sources, including Salesforce data.

Tableau Products:

* Tableau Prep: Prepare data for analysis in Tableau.
* Tableau Desktop: Access, visualize, and analyze your data.
* Tableau Cloud: A fully hosted cloud-based enterprise-grade analytics platform.
* Tableau Server: A self-hosted platform for creating or hosting visualizations.
* Tableau Mobile: Interact with visualizations on your Tableau Server or Cloud site.
* Tableau Public: Explore, create, and publicly share data visualizations online.
title: Understanding Salesforce Analytics with Tableau
